flowchart TD
    A[cargo check] --> B{Compile OK?}
    B -- No --> C[rustc errors → AppError mapping]
    B -- Yes --> D[cargo clippy --all-targets]
    D --> E{Clippy Clean?}
    E -- No --> F[Block: RUST-LINT-001]
    E -- Yes --> G[cargo fmt --check]
    G --> H[cargo test]
    H --> I{All Pass?}
    I -- No --> F
    I -- Yes --> J[cargo build --release]
    J --> K[Sign + Publish]
